OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FThis evening
OL,6,Fwill be dry with some late sunshine.
OL,7,FThen the rest of the night will be dry
OL,8,Fand clear with some patchy fog and low
OL,9,Fcloud. Patchy frost.
OL,10,
OL,11,CFriday:FDry with some sunshine in the
OL,12,Fmorning. Clouding over from the
OL,13,Fsouthwest in the afternoon with some
OL,14,Fshowery rain extending northeast
OL,15,Flater. Warm.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
